statements: SELECT * FROM Trees WHERE tree_species = 'Oak';
SELECT tree_name, age FROM Trees WHERE age > 50;
SELECT tree_species, COUNT(*) FROM Trees GROUP BY tree_species;
SELECT tree_name, last_checked FROM Trees ORDER BY last_checked DESC;
SELECT AVG(age) FROM Trees;
SELECT tree_name, tree_species, age FROM Trees WHERE tree_species = 'Oak' ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT tree_id, tree_name, care_notes FROM Trees WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY tree_name;
SELECT tree_id, tree_name, age, last_checked FROM Trees WHERE last_checked > '2021-07-01' ORDER BY last_checked DESC, age;
SELECT * FROM Trees WHERE tree_species LIKE '%Maple%' OR tree_species LIKE '%Birch%' ORDER BY tree_id ASC;
SELECT tree_species, COUNT(*) AS total_trees FROM Trees GROUP BY tree_species HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY total_trees DESC;
SELECT * FROM Tree;
SELECT tree_name, tree_species FROM Tree WHERE plantation_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT tree_name FROM Tree ORDER BY tree_species DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT tree_species FROM Tree;
SELECT tree_id, tree_name, plantation_date FROM Tree WHERE tree_name LIKE 'Oak%';
SELECT tree_name, tree_species FROM Tree WHERE tree_species='Oak' ORDER BY tree_name ASC;
SELECT tree_name, plantation_date FROM Tree WHERE plantation_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY plantation_date DESC;

SELECT tree_name, tree_species, maintenance_date, cost FROM Tree JOIN Maintenance ON Tree.tree_id = Maintenance.tree_id WHERE maintenance_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC, cost DESC;
SELECT * FROM Tree WHERE tree_species LIKE '%Maple%' ORDER BY tree_id DESC;
SELECT MAX(cost) AS max_cost, MIN(cost) AS min_cost, AVG(cost) AS avg_cost FROM Maintenance;
SELECT * FROM Tree;
SELECT tree_name, age FROM Tree WHERE age > 10;
SELECT tree_name, species, location FROM Tree ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceRecord WHERE maintenance_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT team_lead, expertise_area FROM TreeCareTeam WHERE member_count > 5 ORDER BY expertise_area ASC;
SELECT * FROM Tree WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY tree_name ASC;
SELECT tree_name, age, species FROM Tree WHERE location='Central Park';
SELECT team_lead, member_count FROM TreeCareTeam WHERE member_count > 5 ORDER BY team_lead DESC;
SELECT t.tree_name, m.maintenance_date, m.worker_name FROM Tree t JOIN MaintenanceRecord m ON t.tree_id = m.tree_id;
SELECT t.tree_name, m.maintenance_date, t.location FROM Tree t JOIN MaintenanceRecord m ON t.tree_id = m.tree_id WHERE m.worker_name='John Doe';
SELECT * FROM TreeCare;
SELECT tree_name, location FROM TreeCare WHERE health_status='Healthy';
SELECT tree_name, location, last_trim_date FROM TreeCare WHERE location='Park';
SELECT * FROM TreeMaintenance ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT tree_id, maintenance_type, duration_hrs FROM TreeMaintenance WHERE duration_hrs > 3 ORDER BY duration_hrs ASC;
SELECT * FROM TreeCare ORDER BY tree_id DESC;
SELECT tree_name, location FROM TreeCare WHERE location = 'Park';
SELECT tree_name, health_status FROM TreeCare WHERE health_status='Good' AND location = 'Garden';
SELECT tree_name, location, last_trim_date FROM TreeCare WHERE last_trim_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT t.tree_name, h.health_description FROM TreeCare t JOIN TreeHealth h ON t.tree_id = h.tree_id;
SELECT * FROM Tree ORDER BY tree_id ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT tree_species, tree_age FROM Tree WHERE tree_age > 20
SELECT tree_species, tree_age FROM Tree WHERE planting_date < '2021-01-01'
SELECT * FROM Tree WHERE tree_species LIKE '%oak%'
SELECT tree_id, tree_species, planting_date FROM Tree ORDER BY planting_date DESC
SELECT tree_species, tree_age FROM Tree WHERE tree_age > 50 ORDER BY tree_age DESC;
SELECT * FROM Tree WHERE tree_species = 'Oak' AND tree_age > 20 ORDER BY planting_date ASC;
SELECT tree_species, tree_age, planting_date FROM Tree WHERE planting_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY tree_species, planting_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(tree_id) AS total_trees, tree_species FROM Tree GROUP BY tree_species HAVING total_trees > 2 ORDER BY total_trees DESC;
SELECT tree_species, MAX(tree_age) AS oldest_age FROM Tree GROUP BY tree_species HAVING oldest_age > 100 ORDER BY oldest_age DESC;
